                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I haven't heard much discussion of these,?and I saw a screenshot that piqued my interest in GoD's leadership system.
<br />

<br />
Apparently leadership points can give you the ability to "mark" mobs with a number above their head that everyone in your group can see.  The possibilities for us in marking the order to attack mobs seemed promising to me.  Has anyone else seen this feature or know much about leadership points?</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://home.att.ne.jp/apple/dmolden/screenshots/pixcol.gif" border="0" />
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=611032" target="_blank" class="postlink">Columbyne Celebfin</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
