                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Belanar wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Well, I guess since I'm not in beta I have no idea if the raid leader needs to be the "raid leader" to get whatever abilities these might be. I was thinking like the group leadership abilities I've heard of, like added regen or mana or letting people see who the MT is attacking.
